{"article_id":"KzdcLRd3SZQFKAqN","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Iran warned President Donald Trump on Thursday against being dragged into all-out war in the Middle East","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"following an attack on Saudi Arabian oil facilities","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"which Washington and Riyadh blame on Tehran .","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"U.S. Secretary of State Mike Pompeo has described the weekend strike","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"that initially halved Saudi oil output","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"as an act of war","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"and has been discussing possible retaliation with Saudi Arabia and other Gulf allies .","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"Trump on Wednesday struck a cautious note ,","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"saying","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"there were many options short of war with Iran ,","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"which denies involvement in the Sept. 14 strikes .","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"He ordered more sanctions on Tehran .","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"Iran 's foreign minister told CNN","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"the Islamic Republic `` wo n't blink ''","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"if it has to defend itself against any U.S. or Saudi military strike ,","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"which","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"he said","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"would lead to `` all-out war . ''","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"Mohammed Javad Zarif earlier accused Pompeo of being part of a so-called `` B-team , ''","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"which","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"Tehran says","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"includes Saudi Arabia 's crown prince","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"and is trying to dupe Trump into opting for war .","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"Pompeo said on Wednesday","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"that the attack was `` of a scale","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"we 've just not seen before . ''","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"`` The Saudis were the nation","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"that were attacked .","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"It was on their soil .","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"It was an act of war against them directly , ''","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"he told reporters","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"before meeting Saudi Crown Prince Mohammed bin Salman .","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"Riyadh ,","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"which described the assault as a `` test of global will , ''","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"on Wednesday displayed the remnants of 25 Iranian drones and missiles","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"it said","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"were used in the strike","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"as undeniable evidence of Iranian aggression .","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"The Saudi ambassador to Berlin said","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"`` everything is on the table , ''","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"telling Deutschlandfunk radio","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"that options need to be discussed carefully .","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"The United Arab Emirates on Thursday followed its main Arab ally Saudi Arabia","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"in announcing","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"it was joining a global maritime security coalition","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"that Washington has been trying to build since a series of explosions on oil tankers in Gulf waters in recent months","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"that were also blamed on Tehran .","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"Pompeo ,","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"who arrived in the UAE from Saudi Arabia on Thursday for talks with Abu Dhabi 's crown prince ,","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"welcomed the move on Twitter :","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"`` Recent events underscore the importance","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"of protecting global commerce and freedom of navigation . ''","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"Yemen 's Iran-aligned Houthi movement ,","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"which is battling a Saudi-led military coalition ,","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"claimed responsibility for the assault on two Saudi oil plants ,","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"including the world 's largest processing facility .","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"U.S. and Saudi officials rejected the claim ,","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"the attack had not come from the south .","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"Fellow Gulf OPEC producer Kuwait ,","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"which said earlier this week","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"it was investigating the detection of a drone over its territory ,","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"has put its oil sector on high alert","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"and raised security to the highest level as a precautionary measure .","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"Oil prices ,","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"which soared","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"following the attack ,","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"steadied","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"after Saudi Arabia pledged to restore full production by the end of the month .","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"Proof of Iranian responsibility , and evidence","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"that the attack was launched from Iranian territory ,","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"could pressure Riyadh and Washington ,","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"which want to curb Iranian influence in the region ,","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"into a response .","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"Trump has previously said","depth":6},{"id":75,"text":"he does not want war","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"and is coordinating with Gulf and European states .","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"Pompeo said","depth":6},{"id":78,"text":"the attacks would be a major focus of next week 's annual U.N. General Assembly meeting","depth":6},{"id":79,"text":"and suggested","depth":6},{"id":80,"text":"Riyadh could make its case there .","depth":6},{"id":81,"text":"Iran 's Zarif accused Pompeo of trying to `` dodge a U.S. obligation ''","depth":6},{"id":82,"text":"to issue visas for Iran 's U.N. delegates .","depth":6},{"id":83,"text":"Tehran has said","depth":6},{"id":84,"text":"the U.S. accusations were part of Washington 's `` maximum pressure '' policy on the Islamic Republic","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"to force Iran to renegotiate a 2015 nuclear deal with world powers ,","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"which Trump exited last year ,","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"reimposing sanctions .","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"France ,","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"which is trying to salvage the deal ,","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"said","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"the New York gathering presented a chance","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"to de-escalate tensions .","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"`` When missiles hit another country","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"it is an act of war ,","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"but we have to go back to the principle of de-escalation , ''","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"French foreign minister Jean-Yves Le Drian said .","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"`` There is an international investigation ,","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"let 's wait for its results . ''","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"The French army sent seven experts to Saudi Arabia","depth":7},{"id":100,"text":"to join the investigation .","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"U.N. officials","depth":7},{"id":102,"text":"monitoring sanctions on Iran and Yemen","depth":7},{"id":103,"text":"are also helping probe the attack ,","depth":7},{"id":104,"text":"which exposed gaps in Saudi air defenses","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"despite billions","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"spent on Western military hardware .","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"U.S. efforts","depth":7},{"id":108,"text":"to bring about a U.N. Security Council response","depth":7},{"id":109,"text":"looked unlikely to succeed","depth":6},{"id":110,"text":"as Russia and China have veto powers","depth":6},{"id":111,"text":"and were expected to shield Iran .","depth":6},{"id":112,"text":"Washington and its Gulf allies want Iran to stop supporting regional proxies ,","depth":6},{"id":113,"text":"including in Yemen , Iraq and Lebanon ,","depth":6},{"id":114,"text":"as well as to put more limitations on its nuclear and missile programs .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":229,"left":156,"right":228,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":156,"left":132,"right":155,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":132,"left":121,"right":131,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":121,"left":117,"right":120,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":117,"left":0,"right":116,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":116,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":120,"left":119,"right":6,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":119,"left":118,"right":5,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":118,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":131,"left":125,"right":130,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":125,"left":124,"right":11,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":124,"left":7,"right":123,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":123,"left":8,"right":122,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":122,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":130,"left":12,"right":129,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":129,"left":13,"right":128,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":128,"left":14,"right":127,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":127,"left":126,"right":17,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":126,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":155,"left":145,"right":154,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":145,"left":136,"right":144,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":136,"left":18,"right":135,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":135,"left":134,"right":22,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":134,"left":133,"right":21,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":133,"left":19,"right":20,"relation":"attribution","n